messages.content: You are tasked with creating a structured output from the provided user message.

Files:
- articles/routers.go

Explanation:
- In hello.go the call articles.ArticlesAnonymousRegister(v1.Group("/articles")) registers the anonymous (no-auth) article routes.
- I searched the codebase and found the ArticlesAnonymousRegister function implemented in articles/routers.go (it starts at line 22). That same file also contains the handler implementations wired by that register function: ArticleList, ArticleRetrieve and ArticleCommentList (as well as other article-related handlers and TagList).
- Therefore articles/routers.go is the file that contains the implementation of articles.ArticlesAnonymousRegister and the route handler functions it registers.
